        "In an effort to enhance the model's accuracy, several adjustments were made to the code. Firstly, the model's architecture was augmented by incorporating additional convolutional layers, each with increased complexity in terms of filter counts, along with a denser layer boasting more neurons. This expanded architecture aims to improve the model's capacity to capture intricate patterns within the data. Furthermore, an EarlyStopping callback was introduced, configured to monitor the validation loss and terminate training if no improvement is observed for a set number of epochs, thus preventing overfitting. These modifications are expected to contribute to a more robust and accurate model by leveraging deeper architectures and implementing a strategy to prevent overfitting during training."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "7DmfjH6qo2Hp"
